Join Mike's talk tomorrow.

00:19:05.660 --> 00:19:07.940
And next up we have
Serena and Moonlit

00:19:07.940 --> 00:19:10.930
who's going to take you on
monetization adventures.

00:19:10.930 --> 00:19:11.430
Thank you.

00:19:11.430 --> 00:19:11.790
SAM COSTER: Awesome.

00:19:11.790 --> 00:19:12.290
Thank you.

