00:32:40.910 --> 00:32:44.030
Let's tie this back
to design principles.

00:32:44.030 --> 00:32:47.890
First, the ad unit reinforces
the core game mechanic

00:32:47.890 --> 00:32:49.330
of battles.

00:32:49.330 --> 00:32:52.240
Second, the reward also scales.

00:32:52.240 --> 00:32:54.770
Because it's applied
as a percentage,

00:32:54.770 --> 00:32:57.760
