00:49:05.320 --> 00:49:06.850
You can test out
what things work,

00:49:06.850 --> 00:49:09.320
what things don't work
without a lot of integration.

00:49:09.320 --> 00:49:13.620
Number two, you can
supplement that IAP revenue

00:49:13.620 --> 00:49:18.010
with the rewarded and
probably grow your IAP

00:49:18.010 --> 00:49:20.140
if you do this right.

00:49:20.140 --> 00:49:22.150
And then number three,
our smart segmentation

00:49:22.150 --> 00:49:23.830
offering-- now it's a checkbox.

00:49:23.830 --> 00:49:24.730
It's that simple.

00:49:24.730 --> 00:49:26.530
Don't put any of
your IAP at risk.

00:49:26.530 --> 00:49:29.020
And you have a
chance to monetize

00:49:29.020 --> 00:49:31.730
90% plus of your users
who aren't spending.

00:49:31.730 --> 00:49:33.250
So it's a real win.

